      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "It is not good to accept the person of the wicked.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " To \"accept the person\" is to show partiality, to be guided in judgment, not by the facts of a case, or the abstract principles of right or wrong, but by extraneous considerations, as a man's appearance, manners, fortune, family. (For the expression, comp. ",
        "children": []
